            "voted_up": false,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.4761904776096344,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "\nWanted to enjoy FIFA 22 but it’s a massive disappointment. Ultimate Team is pure pay-to-win; you either spend real money or get crushed by those who do. The scripting is obvious and infuriating — momentum swings and ridiculous goals ruin every match.\n\nGameplay feels stiff and repetitive, Career Mode is boring and outdated, and the whole thing lacks soul. Years later, it just feels abandoned."
